00:04:15.090 --> 00:04:18.230
First rule everything in
it had to be interesting.

00:04:18.230 --> 00:04:20.320
Not a bad standard.

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:22.570
That was the first thing
I learned from her.

00:04:22.570 --> 00:04:24.440
I kind of never thought
of that actually,

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:28.490
I was sort of a truth
in beauty guy, right?

00:04:28.490 --> 00:04:29.790
Interesting.

00:04:29.790 --> 00:04:31.470
And, the other was it had to
have a character with red hair.

00:04:31.470 --> 00:04:34.370
Because, my daughter
is a ginger, alright.

00:04:34.370 --> 00:04:35.780
And, if you've read
the books you know

00:04:35.780 --> 00:04:38.870
that there is indeed a
red headed character.

00:04:38.870 --> 00:04:41.730
We did this for 90 days I
had no intention, whatsoever,

00:04:41.730 --> 00:04:43.180
