00:04:43.180 --> 00:04:45.010
I was lying to my kid.

00:04:45.010 --> 00:04:50.080
We were all just getting in really
good shape and having some fun.

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:52.930
But, after 90 days past and the
bicycle went into the garage.

00:04:52.930 --> 00:04:55.410
I decided I would take some notes.

00:04:55.410 --> 00:04:58.730
I thought maybe, you know, we've
come up with a lot of stuff here.

00:04:58.730 --> 00:05:02.420
Why don't I write it
down maybe for later use?

00:05:02.420 --> 00:05:06.740
Because the book as I said, I was
writing, was kind of on oxygen.

00:05:06.740 --> 00:05:09.040
And, I looked up a
couple of days later

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:11.600
