spaced pages of notes.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:16.990
Like every detail of
a very long novel

00:05:16.990 --> 00:05:22.100
and then quick summaries
of books two and three.

00:05:22.100 --> 00:05:23.870
It was just an avalanche of stuff.

00:05:23.870 --> 00:05:26.530
And, you know, I can't really
account for it accept to say

00:05:26.530 --> 00:05:29.000
that my daughter and I we
just had good chemistry.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:31.340
And, at some level she
silenced my inner critic.

00:05:31.340 --> 00:05:34.990
And, I also was, as a teacher
of creative writing one

00:05:34.990 --> 00:05:37.720
